war.model

Class ClimateParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • war.model.ClimateParams

  • @Entity
public class ClimateParams
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a combination of Climate Parameters. Includes a year, a CO2 emissions scenario, a climate model, a region, and the name of the climate model in that region.
    Since:
    20th Dec. 2012
    Author:
    Guillaume Prevost
